---
// Travel & Stay — Warren leads (green). Airport facts about Rehoboth, MA
// are real geography; the room block and shuttle details follow.
---

<section id="travel" class="section travel" data-lead="green" aria-labelledby="travel-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow">Travel &amp; Stay</p>
      <h2 id="travel-title">Finding your way to us</h2>
      <p>Rehoboth sits just over the Rhode Island line — easy to reach, and worth lingering in for the weekend.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="travel__grid">
      <article class="travel__panel gg-frame" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="travel__panel-title">Getting Here</h3>
        <dl class="travel__list">
          <div class="travel__row">
            <dt>By air</dt>
            <dd>T.&nbsp;F. Green / Rhode Island (PVD) is about twenty-five minutes out; Boston Logan (BOS) about fifty.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="travel__row">
            <dt>By car</dt>
            <dd>Rehoboth is an easy drive from Providence, Boston, and the Cape. Parking will be plentiful.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="travel__row">
            <dt>Getting about</dt>
            <dd>A shuttle between the hotel block and the celebration is being arranged — details to come.</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </article>

      <article class="travel__panel travel__panel--stay" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="travel__panel-title">Where to Stay</h3>
        <p class="travel__stay-lede">
          We&rsquo;re holding a block of rooms nearby at a friendly rate. Once it&rsquo;s
          confirmed, the hotel, the link, and the booking cutoff will live right here.
        </p>
        <p class="travel__stay-meta">
          <span class="chip" data-tone="green">Room block — coming soon</span>
        </p>
        <a class="gg-btn gg-btn--sm" data-variant="outline" href="#rsvp">Let us know you&rsquo;re coming</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .travel__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(290px, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(var(--space-5), 4vw, var(--space-7));
    align-items: start;
  }

  .travel__panel { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16); }
  .travel__panel-title {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    color: var(--lead-strong);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-h3);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .travel__list { margin: 0; display: grid; gap: var(--space-5); }
  .travel__row { display: grid; gap: 4px; }
  .travel__row dt {
    font-family: var(--font-deco);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-label);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-300);
  }
  .travel__row dd { margin: 0; color: var(--text-body); font-size: var(--fs-body); }

  .travel__panel--stay {
    border: 1px solid var(--line-gold);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: clamp(var(--space-5), 4vw, var(--space-7));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    background:
      linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(141, 107, 49, 0.10), transparent 70%),
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
  }
  .travel__stay-lede { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; max-width: 46ch; }
  .travel__stay-meta { margin: 0; }
</style>
